{"tid":767943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委內瑞拉發生針對馬杜羅襲擊　當局拘捕多名可疑人士","createTime":"2018-08-05T03:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T03:51:51.000Z","uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7332e5df8db4a1cac82b3cfcf4ed2c5d3a09ee","tid":767943,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:48:27.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅發表演說時，有無人機飛到他面前發生爆炸，馬杜羅沒有受傷，但有七名士兵受傷，他指控哥倫比亞總統桑托斯及國內極右翼分子策劃襲擊，已經拘捕及扣留多名懷疑策劃襲擊的人士。內政部表示，部分策劃者居住在美國及哥倫比亞。<br />\n<br />\n在當地星期六下午，馬杜羅出席首都加拉加斯一場軍隊紀念活動，電視直播他的講話時，現場突然發生爆炸，馬杜羅表現錯愕，他沒有受傷，隨即與多名官員撤離，直播亦中斷，原本排出方陣步操的軍人慌忙逃生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410694-20180805.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410694-20180805.htm&d=OF85xTxwdB8Jrd18ODRdZ5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fc39f2ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410694-20180805.htm&h=9da432c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410694-20180805.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f4feeef11215c1a76c39978b0dcee61d502e343d","tid":767943,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:49:24.000Z","msg":"無人機襲擊範例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0effbea6fac8bd2c75eff58d680569dea1d6d971","tid":767943,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:51:51.000Z","msg":"無人機遲早會被人禁 <br />\n(或者被人用法律方法癱瘓 好像一大堆可索償條款 無人敢用)<br />\n<br />\n私隱,安全 好多野都可以打"}]}